As discussed, attached are the title transfer documents we have for Epstein's New York, Palm Beach, and Virgin Islands 
residences. I've also included the articles of incorporation for four of the relevant entities referenced in the transfer 
documents. It appears that we obtained at least some of these documents pursuant to grand jury subpoenas. Let me 
know if you need us to distinguish between the documents that we found through without a subpoena and those we 
obtained via subpoena. 
We do not have documents for the New Mexico property, as far as I can tell, but I'll chat with the team about tracking 
those down. Please let us know if there are any other materials you need us to find as well. 
Thanks, 
EFTA00030125
